---
title: Middle Eastern Chermoula Roast Pumpkin Bowl with Pearl Couscous & Garlic Dip
description: A roast pumpkin bowl sounds so nourishing and refreshing especially when there’s some warm Middle Eastern flavours. The
touch of chermoula really brings everything together and adds an extra burst of flavour to the pearl couscous. We’re feeling
rejuvenated already!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
